channel.title: Problem with Run.bat
channel.description:
Hey guys! I have recently downloaded the RuneEclipse source and client to test it out. It has a lot of potential so I am going to continue working on it. However I do have a problem. When I change all of the dialogue and server names and owner names and etc to my own and compile I get this error. Could you guys please tell me how to fix this. I am currently on holiday and using my sisters laptop, I don't remember this happening on my home PC but it happens on my sisters laptop.
[img]http://i.imgur.com/zGRHs.png[/img]
EDIT: I have just been outside and shut down the laptop, I have just tried to open the server without compiling and it has worked, This is ok I guess. Do you guys know how to fix it? I don't want to have to restart the laptop every time I change something :/
